1) Install NodeJS
2) open Node.js command prompt
3) set root folder path Ex:- cd Angular
4) Create a new workspace and an initial application
    ng new ApplicationTableAccess
5) Install all required npm packages by running command from the command line in the project root folder (where the package.json is located)
    npm install -g @angular/cli
6) Start the application by running
       ng serve --open
           (or)
       ng serve --port 3000
       


Tutorial Page
https://angular.io/tutorial/toh-pt0

